Air Quality - https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/allegheny-county-air-quality
Crime Incidents - https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/monthly-criminal-activity-dashboard/resource/bd41992a-987a-4cca-8798-fbe1cd946b07
Parks - https://data.wprdc.org/dataset/playgrounds/resource/47350364-44a8-4d15-b6e0-5f79ddff9367

The purpose of this github repo is a combination of three metrics: Air Quality, Park access, and crime, in order to determine what might be the best neighborhood within Pittsburgh
Each file has an independent way of approcahing data clean up and presentation, and then a combined file that rates all of the data on a Min-Max normalization. 
Squirrel Hill South came out to be the best neighborhood according to our data. 
